	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />try making thebyte into an unsigned long and using this ASM
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">__asm &#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;push eax<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;mov eax, offset starthex<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;mov eax, &#91;eax&#93;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;mov thebyte, eax<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;pop eax<br />&#125;</div>
<br />
<br />Basically your code fragment only reads one byte of data when you want to read 4 bytes of data (i.e. one unsigned long worth)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


